ature-icon\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-shipping-fast\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3>Fast Delivery</h3>\n                    <p>Free shipping on orders over $50. Get your products delivered within 2-3 business days.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                    <div class=\"feature-icon\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3>Secure Payment</h3>\n                    <p>Your payment information is safe with us. We use industry-standard encryption.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                    <div class=\"feature-icon\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-headset\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3>24/7 Support</h3>\n                    <p>Our customer service team is available round the clock to assist you with any queries.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-card\">\n                    <div class=\"feature-icon\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-undo-alt\"></i>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3>Easy Returns</h3>\n                    <p>Not satisfied with your purchase? Return it within 30 days for a full refund.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- About Section -->\n        <section>\n            <div class=\"about-container\">\n                <div class=\"about-content\">\n                    <h2>About Us</h2>\n                    <p>We are a passionate team dedicated to providing high-quality products and exceptional customer service. Our journey began in 2010 with a simple mission: to make premium products accessible to everyone.</p>\n                    <p>Over the years, we\'ve grown from a small startup to a trusted brand with customers worldwide. We carefully curate our product selection to ensure we offer only the best items that meet our strict quality standards.</p>\n                    <p>Our commitment to sustainability and ethical business practices sets us apart. We work closely with our suppliers to ensure fair working conditions and minimize our environmental impact.</p>\n                    <p>Thank you for choosing us. We\'re honored to be part of your shopping experience and look forward to serving you for years to come.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"about-image\">\n                    <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1470&q=80\" alt=\"Our Team\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Footer -->\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"footer-content\">\n                <div class=\"footer-logo\">ShopEase</div>\n                <div class=\"footer-links\">\n                    <a href=\"#\">Home</a>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Products</a>\n                    <a href=\"#\">About</a>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Contact</a>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a>\n                    <a href=\"#\">Terms of Service</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"social-icons\">\n                    <a href=\"#\"><i class=\"fab fa-facebook-f\"></i></a>\n                    <a href=\"#\"><i class=\"fab fa-twitter\"></i></a>\n                    <a href=\"#\"><i class=\"fab fa-instagram\"></i></a>\n                    <a href=\"#\"><i class=\"fab fa-pinterest\"></i></a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"copyright\">\n                    &copy; 2023 ShopEase. All rights reserved.\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Slider functionality\n        document.addEventListener(\'DOMContentLoaded\', function() {\n            const slider = document.querySelector(\'.slider\');\n            const slides = document.querySelectorAll(\'.slide\');\n            const dots = document.querySelectorAll(\'.slider-dot\');\n            const prevArrow = document.querySelector(\'.slider-arrow.prev\');\n            const nextArrow = document.querySelector(\'.slider-arrow.next\');\n            \n            let currentSlide = 0;\n            const slideCount = slides.length;\n            let slideInterval;\n            \n            // Initialize slider\n            function initSlider() {\n                updateSlider();\n                startSlideInterval();\n                \n                // Add event listeners\n                prevArrow.addEventListener(\'click\', showPrevSlide);\n                nextArrow.addEventListener(\'click\', showNextSlide);\n                \n                dots.forEach(dot => {\n                    dot.addEventListener(\'click\', function() {\n                        currentSlide = parseInt(this.getAttribute(\'data-slide\'));\n                        updateSlider();\n                        resetSlideInterval();\n                    });\n                });\n            }\n            \n            // Update slider position and active dot\n            function updateSlider() {\n                slider.style.transform = `translateX(-${currentSlide * 25}%)`;\n                \n                // Update active dot\n                dots.forEach(dot => dot.classList.remove(\'active\'));\n                dots[currentSlide].classList.add(\'active\');\n            }\n            \n            // Show next slide\n            function showNextSlide() {\n                currentSlide = (currentSlide + 1) % slideCount;\n                updateSlider();\n                resetSlideInterval();\n            }\n            \n            // Show previous slide\n            function showPrevSlide() {\n                currentSlide = (currentSlide - 1 + slideCount) % slideCount;\n                updateSlider();\n                resetSlideInterval();\n            }\n            \n            // Start automatic slide interval\n            function startSlideInterval() {\n                slideInterval = setInterval(showNextSlide, 4000);\n            }\n            \n            // Reset slide interval\n            function resetSlideInterval() {\n                clearInterval(slideInterval);\n                startSlideInterval();\n            }\n            \n            // Initialize the slider\n            initSlider();\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Hura-Ganies - Featured Product</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css\">\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            font-family: \'Segoe UI\', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n        }\n\n        :root {\n            --dark-bg: #0a0f0d;\n            --dark-card: #111715;\n            --accent-green: #2a9d8f;\n            --accent-green-light: #4ecdc4;\n            --accent-green-dark: #1d6f65;\n            --text-light: #e9f5db;\n            --text-gray: #8a9a8a;\n            --featured-glow: rgba(42, 157, 143, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        body {\n            background-color: var(--dark-bg);\n            color: var(--text-light);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            padding: 2rem;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            min-height: 100vh;\n        }\n\n        .featured-section {\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            width: 100%;\n        }\n\n        .featured-title {\n            text-align: center;\n            mar